24
00:01:17,200 --> 00:01:19,860
 by NABH or NABL.

25
00:01:19,860 --> 00:01:23,240
 The treatment must be inpatient and medically necessary.

26
00:01:23,240 --> 00:01:28,840
 The hospital should have at least five beds, a qualified Ayush doctor and maintain daily

27
