 inpatient programme.

32
00:01:47,400 --> 00:01:49,880
 Now what is not covered in Ayush?

33
00:01:50,080 --> 00:01:57,080
 OPD consultations at local clinics, spa treatments, wellness retreats or casual yoga sessions,

34
